            />
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.1.0</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Fixed crash</strong> - Resolved SwiftUI/AppKit race condition that caused crashes after extended uptime</li>
                    <li><strong>Fixed window gaps</strong> - Windows now snap perfectly with no pixel gaps on multi-monitor setups</li>
                    <li><strong>Auto-updates</strong> - Added Sparkle for automatic update notifications</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
